No, the units are meant to be exactly 0.005 tons/unit. Anything else is rounding error. You can find the definitions yourself:

GameData/Squad/Resources/ResourcesGeneric.cfg:

    RESOURCE_DEFINITION{  name = LiquidFuel  density = 0.005  unitCost = 0.8  flowMode = STACK_PRIORITY_SEARCH  transfer = PUMP  isTweakable = true}RESOURCE_DEFINITION{  name = Oxidizer  density = 0.005  unitCost = 0.18  flowMode = STACK_PRIORITY_SEARCH  transfer = PUMP  isTweakable = true}
